<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Lambda - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/lambda/</link><description>Lambda - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/lambda/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Java语言特性与关键词</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/java%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/java%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="java语言特性与关键词">Java语言特性与关键词</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Java通过面向对象、泛型、Lambda表达式和Stream API四大核心机制，实现了类型安全与表达能力的平衡，其中泛型编译期擦除和Lambda的方法引用转换是理解底层实现的关键。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="java通过面向对象泛型lambda和stream四大机制实现类型安全与表达能力的平衡">Java通过面向对象、泛型、Lambda和Stream四大机制实现类型安全与表达能力的平衡</h2>
<h3 id="面向对象封装继承多态是代码组织的基础范式">面向对象：封装、继承、多态是代码组织的基础范式</h3>
<p>Java的面向对象并非纯粹（保留基本类型和静态方法），而是在工程实践中权衡后的设计：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>实现方式</th>
          <th>关键约束</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>封装</td>
          <td>访问修饰符 + 包机制</td>
          <td><code>private</code>仅在类内，<code>protected</code>含子类和同包</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>继承</td>
          <td>单继承（类）、多实现（接口）</td>
          <td>避免菱形继承问题</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>多态</td>
          <td>虚方法表 + 动态绑定</td>
          <td><code>final</code>/<code>static</code>/<code>private</code>方法不参与动态绑定</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 多态的本质：运行时根据实际类型调用方法</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">Animal</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">speak</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">Dog</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">extends</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Animal</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nd">@Override</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">speak</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">System</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">out</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;wang&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">Animal</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">a</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Dog</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">speak</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">运行时绑定到</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Dog</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">speak</span><span class="p">()</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="泛型编译期类型擦除换取兼容性运行时无泛型信息">泛型：编译期类型擦除换取兼容性，运行时无泛型信息</h3>
<p>泛型的设计目标是编译期类型检查，而非运行期性能优化。</p>
<p><strong>类型擦除规则</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><code>List&lt;String&gt;</code> 和 <code>List&lt;Integer&gt;</code> 运行时都是 <code>List</code></li>
<li>泛型参数替换为上限（无上限则替换为 <code>Object</code>）</li>
<li>编译器插入强制类型转换代码</li>
</ul>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 擦除前</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">List</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">String</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">list</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ArrayList</span><span class="o">&lt;&gt;</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">list</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">add</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;hello&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">s</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">list</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">0</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 擦除后（JVM看到的字节码）</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">List</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">list</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ArrayList</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">list</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">add</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;hello&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">s</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">String</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">list</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">0</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="o">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">编译器插入强转</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
